xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>-truncated</html:span> types</fr:link>. By analogy, we shall also refer to maps as <fr:em><fr:strong>contractible</fr:strong></fr:em> when their fibers are; we shall refer to maps as <fr:em><fr:strong>propositional</fr:strong></fr:em> when their fibers are <fr:link
